IN LOVING MEMORY OF
RONALD TURNER, DAUGHTER CHERIE
& SON GARRY
ALL SADLY MISSED
NEVER FORGOTTEN"Ż
║In fondest memory of my husband
TREVOR PRYTHERCH JONES
of Flint
Who spent many happy years,
both working and at leisure in Llandudno.
Always in my thoughts. Your loving wife Doreen."└
ŻJOHN HENRY RIMMER (Johnny)
1933 - 1998
Born and lived in Liverpool for 31 years
Hundred End Lancashire 33 years
Llandudno was dear to his heart
Always in my thoughts,
loving wife Gwen"┬
